Ephyflow Extension for Epiphany by Matt Read, 2010
http://github.com/MattRead/Ephyflow

This extension integrates the Steadyflow download manager with Epiphany.

INSTALLATION

In order for seed extensions to work in epiphany you need to have both the gir1.0-webkit-1.0
and gir1.0-soup-2.4 installed.

Just copy `ephyflow.js` and `ephyflow.ephy-extension` to `~/.gnome2/epiphany/extensions/`.
Then enable the extension in the Extension Manager.

USAGE

Steadyflow has to be open for this extension to work.

Simply clicking on a link to a download file, will add the download to Steadyflow.
